      "countAsQuest:1": 1,
      "desc:8": "As you may have noticed, graves only spawn skeletons.\n\nTo get some other mobs, which you may not need but certainly want, you\u0027ll have to make a dark room. \n\nGravel, Drowning, and Dirt creepers all need a dark room, and so do Zombie Villagers and Witches.\n\n\n[note]Note: spawning code makes sure that the spawned mob cannot collide with anything around it. As the mob has some offset from the centre of the block, that means that a 1 by 2 room is horribly inefficient for spawning.\n\nA 2 by 2 by 2 will serve much better, and the bigger you make it the more common successful spawning will be, as well as the less block you need to make it dark permanently. [/note]",
